premise_source_doc_sentence: Istanbul is a transcontinental city in Eurasia , straddling the Bosphorus strait  (  which separates Europe and Asia  )  between the Sea of Marmara and the Black Sea .
Istanbul is one of the world 's most populous cities and ranks as the world 's 7th-largest city proper and the largest European city .
Considered a global city , Istanbul has one of the fastest-growing metropolitan economies in the world .

The use of `` global city '' , as opposed to `` megacity '' , was popularized by sociologist Saskia Sassen in her 1991 work , The Global City : New York , London , Tokyo ; although the term `` world city '' , which refers to cities involved with large amounts of global business , dates to at least the May 1886 description of Liverpool , by The Illustrated London News .
A world city is a city deemed to be an important node point in the global economic system .
